                  <title ref="" type="supplied">Martyrdom of <persName ref="">Mamas</persName>, his father <persName ref="">Theodotus</persName>, and his mother <persName ref="">Rufina</persName></title>
                  <rubric xml:lang="syr">ܬܘܒ ܬܫܥܝܬܐ ܐܘܟܝܬ ܣܗܕܘܬܐ ܕܩܕܝܫܐ ܡܪܝ ܡܐܡܐ. ܘܐܒܘܗܝ ܬܐܘܕܘܛܘܣ. ܘܐܢܬܬܗ ܪܘܦܝܢܐ.<locus from="303a"/></rubric>
