                    <title ref="" type="supplied">Martyrdom of <listPerson><person><persName ref="">the Praepositus Romulus </persName> (<quote xml:lang="syr"><persName ref="">ܪܘܡܝܠܘܣ ܐܦܪܘܦܣܛܝܣ</persName></quote></person></listPerson> or <quote xml:lang="syr"><persName ref="">ܦܪܐܦܝܣܛܝܣ ܪܘܡܠܘܣ</persName></quote>) under <persName ref="">Trajan</persName>; and of the <persName ref="">Comes Eudoxius, surnamed Marianus</persName> (<quote xml:lang="syr"><persName ref="">ܐܒܕܘܟܣܝܘܣ ܗ̇ܘ ܕܡܬܟ݁ܢܐ ܡܪܝܐܢܣ</persName></quote>), and his son <persName ref="">Macarius</persName>, under <persName ref="">Diocletian</persName>.</title>
