                    <rubric xml:lang="syr">ܬܫܥܝܬܐ ܕܥܠ ܫܘܢ̇ܝܗ̇ ܕܝ̇ܠܕܬ̇ ܐܠܗܐ̣ ܐܡܐ ܡܒܪܟܬܐ<locus from="449a" to="449a"/></rubric>
                    <note>It is imperfect at the beginning and towards the end.<!-- This should go in the physical description as well. --></note>
                    <note>See <bibl>Wright's Contributions to the Apocryphal Literature of the N. T., pp. 10 and <foreign xml:lang="syr">ܠܓ</foreign>.</bibl></note>
                  </msItem>
